o reproductive health services.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sheila McParland","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89543362"},{"created_at":"2014-04-12T03:22:02Z","content":"The rights over an individuals body is thier own.  It is not to be dictated by the state","like_count":0,"author_name":"Steve Leadbeater","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89426421"},{"created_at":"2014-03-10T03:35:36Z","content":"Every woman deserves the right","like_count":0,"author_name":"lindsay ahern","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/85128174"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T01:30:48Z","content":"Not all birth control is 100% effective. Not all sexual relations are consentual. Not everyone shares the same beliefs, religious or otherwise. Let them choose what is best for them on their own. Everyone needs equal opportunity to decide what is best for themselves. This issue affects everyone, no matter their age, gender identity, sexual orientation, because until we are all equal, we all need to fight for those who have their rights taken away from them. For a woman like myself, and for all whom this affects, the right to a safe, legal, and easily accessible abortion is vital. Whether I will need the service one day or not.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lise Arsenault","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89316432"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T03:35:05Z","content":"Because women deserve the right to make decisions about their own reproductive decisions.","like_count":0,"author_name":"J. Lynn Stapleton ","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/6567557"},{"created_at":"2014-03-28T13:35:21Z","content":"women have to have the choice to be mother or not. services \u00e9qual security and acces equal choice. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Nathalie Monique Dupuis","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/87723352"},{"created_at":"2014-03-11T16:37:44Z","content":"It's my body.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Mathea Mitchell","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/85308932"},{"created_at":"2014-03-10T19:04:05Z","content":"It is the law in Canada that Medicare should pay for this procedure for women. The NB Government must follow the law!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Allison Webster","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/20577380"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T17:28:56Z","content":"Woman have the right to CHOOSE!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Stacy Corbin","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89635681"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T18:43:17Z","content":"How is this not? Freedom of choice!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jimmy Sauvageau","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89646123"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T23:24:30Z","content":"Women's rights are human rights.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Emma Hawkins","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89306685"},{"created_at":"2014-03-25T21:01:22Z","content":"It's sometimes an important physical or mental health or a social issue... A choice to not having a child is sometimes the best choice for everybody, the only way to avoid dramas.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Maryse Pitre","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/87317178"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T22:08:13Z","content":"family planning is essential to women's well being and prosperity","like_count":0,"author_name":"Marcelle Fletcher","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/45094558"},{"created_at":"2014-03-10T21:59:17Z","content":"The right to choose is key to women's health!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Michelle Gill","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/85220619"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T20:44:52Z","content":"I grew up in Fredericton and remember driving by that clinic where the anti-abortionists would stand and wave signs saying horrible things about women who wanted an abortion.  I am saddened and disgusted to know that those people have won.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jennifer Holyoke","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89552217"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T22:00:03Z","content":"As a family doctor in PEI, I want to see safe, legal and affordable options for all aspects of reproductive health care for all Canadian women, including access to therapeutic abortions.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jenni Zelin","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89556367"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T02:35:33Z","content":"This is ridiculous. I would definitely donate money on an annual basis to keep the clinic open.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Cynthia Craig","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89320677"},{"created_at":"2014-04-12T13:25:21Z","content":"This is a necessity","like_count":0,"author_name":"Eileen Warren","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/14243692"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T05:41:43Z","content":"Women need to have control of their own bodies and have reproductive choices.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jacquie Stinson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37911999"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T16:11:31Z","content":"Freedom of choice.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Steve Adamson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89627659"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T20:31:59Z","content":"People need access to safe affordable abortions, it is obvious that someone who cannot afford an abortion costing almost $2000 (which will be the only option within NB if the Morgentaler clinic is closed) cannot afford to raise a child. if the clinic is closed many people will realize NB isn't a place that is concerned with the well being of its people. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Venita Williston","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89279448"},{"created_at":"2014-04-16T13:38:22Z","content":"Because all people with uteruses in Canada need access to safe, accessible abortions. Because reducing abortion access reduces the number of safe abortions sought but not the number of abortions sought. Because requiring two doctors to deem an abortion medically necessary is not only traumatic and ridiculous, but it goes against the rights of people who have uteruses. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Abigail Kidd","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/31993499"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T22:43:25Z","content":"I as a male do not get to choose what a woman can do with her body. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Trevor Muxworthy","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89298750"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T02:23:02Z","content":"I have had to go to the Morgentaler Clinic before.  Seeing as how PEI has no abortion clinic, this was the closest and discreet place where women could go and have this procedure done without discrimination.  This clinic made me feel comfortable with the decision I made, and passed no judgement upon those using the facilities.  I am saddened to hear that the clinic is closing.  Maybe this petition will help","like_count":0,"author_name":"Stephanie B","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89319870"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T11:46:53Z","content":"women have the right to choose and have this medical services paid for by the province","like_count":0,"author_name":"Robichaud Monique","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89356320"},{"created_at":"2014-03-10T16:19:57Z","content":"Who made you God to decide what is right for her?","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jesse Fearon","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/3595442"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T15:25:36Z","content":"Safe medical abortions must be provided to all women across our country. \"Medical Necessity\" is not the only reason for abortion - there are sexual assaults occurring everyday that go unreported and can end up in unplanned pregnancy. Do you think that those women deserve the right to choose?! Furthermore, having worked in the legal profession for several years, almost every day I see children whose parents did not want them. So many children are living in situations where their parents have no money to feed or house them, provide them with clean clothes, or give them the things that their growing bodies and minds need. These kids end up having no childhood - they are consistently poked and prodded by Social Services, and tossed around the system (ex. foster care, temporary placement, etc.). Life is not black and white, ever. Anyone who does not believe in this procedure has obviously not seen the outcome of a child unwanted. Every child should be wanted, every child should be loved. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jill Smith","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89375266"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T21:08:19Z","content":"It is a person's own choice what they want to do, and they should be given that right and have a safe place where they can go for help.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Karren Williston","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89285028"},{"created_at":"2014-04-28T21:19:20Z","content":"Reproductive rights are human rights","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jane Butler","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/62527958"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T13:38:10Z","content":"Every women should have a choice.  It's no ones else's business what a women wants to do with her own body.  I would certainly rather pay for abortions than welfare!!!!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jenny Lebrun","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89527437"},{"created_at":"2014-03-11T12:47:26Z","content":"Abortion and other family planning services are medical services, and should be covered as such by Medicare. Fund services at the Morgentaler Clinic in Fredericton, as it is in other provinces!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sarah Burke","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/9081866"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T11:45:57Z","content":"Abortion is a womans choice! It is archaic to assume that a woman should have to carry a child because a group of closed minded people should dictate what we can do with our bodies!","like_count":0,"author_name":"tracey matheson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89612771"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T17:10:01Z","content":"It's ridiculous we are the only province where medicare dosen't cover abortions. Why? This is discrimination agains women in N.B. We pay our taxes just like everyone else.  ","li