{"page":3,"prev_page_endpoint":"http://api.change.org/v1/petitions/1459961/reasons?page=2&page_size=500","next_page_endpoint":"http://api.change.org/v1/petitions/1459961/reasons?page=4&page_size=500","total_pages":5,"reasons":[{"created_at":"2014-04-10T21:13:06Z","content":"Women's rights are human rights.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Ashley Avery","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/47207646"},{"created_at":"2014-04-18T15:11:15Z","content":"Because women's health should not suffer because of a the way backwards conservative politics runs our beautiful province. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kyle Smith","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/90106773"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T22:18:51Z","content":"Women should have a choice. Prevent harmful alternatives.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sarah Gorman","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/57385692"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T16:20:39Z","content":"Because an abortion saved my life. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Chloe Lum","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/11763448"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T00:38:40Z","content":"I believe that access to free, safe abortions should constitute basic healthcare for woman and in turn, be a basic right for all women. The fact that freedom to choose is being denied to women in NB is vile. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Krista Ross","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/44600253"},{"created_at":"2014-05-15T00:39:31Z","content":"Because a woman should have the right to choose what she does with her body; it is her temple, not the province's. We're supposed to separate state and religion, yet religion is impeding on women's right to choose. There is a strong correlation between the right of choice and decreased crime rates due to the decrease of unwanted babies that are born, therefore we're not doing anyone any favours by taking that away. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Dana Jamaleddine","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/27248225"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T03:24:27Z","content":"For women, for families, for the community...it is the right thing!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Nancy Ketch","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89323968"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T15:47:11Z","content":"Women deserve a choice! ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kathleen Doucet","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78380751"},{"created_at":"2014-04-12T21:24:24Z","content":"This is a service that needs to be made readily available to all women regardless of the reason for it's need. Closing this clinic will cause a lot of problems that could be far reaching, going decades into the future. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sara O'Toole","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89487432"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T19:09:16Z","content":"All women should have equal access to abortions.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Wendy McPeake","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/9169213"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T17:11:10Z","content":"Every woman should have their rights.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Marielle LeBlanc","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/22879779"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T21:47:02Z","content":"Women should be able to have a choice, it's as simple as that","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jessica Nason","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89290074"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T23:48:00Z","content":"this is a legal right and no government has the right to defy the law.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Krista Steeves","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/30247129"},{"created_at":"2014-04-15T19:17:56Z","content":"My best friend Samatha Goodine wrote a letter to Wes McLean describing what so many of us feel: \"I was embarrassed to say that I am a New Brunswicker, because who would be proud to say that they are from a province that still imposes archaic restrictions on abortions that have been ruled illegal and in direction violation of the Charter of Rights and Freedom (s.7, security of person to be specific, in case anyone forgot). Let me make this clear: the court ruled these restrictions unconstitutional when I was less than a year old. For my entire life the government of New Brunswick has ignored women\u2019s rights.\"\r\n\r\nChange this NOW. For the future of Women's Health and Women's Rights.\r\n\r\n\r\n","like_count":0,"author_name":"Brittany Spencer","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89769921"},{"created_at":"2014-03-11T01:12:38Z","content":"Because I am a woman!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Joanne Manley","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/24910360"},{"created_at":"2014-03-25T19:41:23Z","content":"Toutes les femmes devraient avoir droit aux m\u00eames services, ici, au Canada.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Isabelle D'Ambremont","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/87304707"},{"created_at":"2014-04-15T02:04:37Z","content":"This option needs to be available, and we need to keep Dr. Morgentaler's legacy alive! ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Meagan Dutchak","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89688422"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T14:20:07Z","content":"women should have the right to choose,  it is a basic human right","like_count":0,"author_name":"stephanie boyne","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89369391"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T15:08:54Z","content":"So that people understand, this is NOT just about abortion, it is about a RIGHT to a medical procedure ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Baba Das","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89620950"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T16:46:27Z","content":"Women in NB need access to abortion clinics as women in other provinces do","like_count":0,"author_name":"Janice Langis","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/80487300"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T17:45:46Z","content":"Because i am a women and i deserve to have a choice ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jessica Dickson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/84774265"},{"created_at":"2014-04-15T18:37:06Z","content":"Women have fought long and hard for the right to choose abortion. It is a difficult decision, but if it is not covered women will go to butchers to have it done, or be forced to raise children in poverty","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sue McLean","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/47329991"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T16:01:53Z","content":" I feeling getting rid of this clinic would be talking away our rights (as females) to choose our own paths. \r\n\r\nRape happens.\r\nCondoms break.\r\nMistakes are made. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Mandy Burnham","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89626731"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T07:01:36Z","content":"Our Reproductive Rights must be protected.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Donna Moore","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89508671"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T17:21:26Z","content":"Because every woman should have the right to control her own body and the legal and medical services required to do so.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Barbara Grimmon","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89634663"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T17:40:16Z","content":"My body, my rights. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Brooklynn Collins","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89323532"},{"created_at":"2014-03-24T15:30:58Z","content":"Respect the law! Every woman has the constitutional right to control her own reproduction. New Brunswick discriminates against women.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Michele Landsberg","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/2493916"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T03:11:31Z","content":"Because I am a woman in Canada that lived on the east coast for 3 years, I feel it is a necessity to have these clinics available to all women everywhere for their safety. PRO-CHOICE. CARE FOR THE CHILDREN ALREADY HERE DAMNIT.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Victoria Brown","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/16915048"},{"created_at":"2014-04-19T01:59:08Z","content":"Women need and deserve choice\r\n","like_count":0,"author_name":"Christine Noble Seller","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/87581884"},{"created_at":"2014-04-15T12:29:06Z","content":"It is abhorent that in 2014 someone elses religious beliefs are making decisions about whats right and whats wrong on MY body. Just shows how backwards this province is and makes us want to leave even more.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jessica Durette","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/61569763"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T01:14:13Z","content":"Reproductive health services are essential services,  They must be funded.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Anna Maranta","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/1658093"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T22:11:49Z","content":"Her body, her choice.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Curtis Runstedler","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89673179"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T05:59:04Z","content":"Praying for the safety of women in NB and PEI affected by this.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Emily Cameron","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/8486655"},{"created_at":"2014-04-16T00:23:04Z","content":"because everyone has a right to decide what happens to their body!!!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Shawna McCurdy","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89799651"},{"created_at":"2014-04-17T03:19:16Z","content":"It is VITAL that women should have access to medically regulated abortions, and that it be their choice whether or not to have one. Without this clinic, some women will be forced to resort to undergoing un-regulated and risky procedures, or trying to terminate pregnancies themselves. Or, they might be forced to stay in abusive relationships they could have otherwise left. I am shocked that any Canadian government would be so reckless as to let this happen... we need more safe abortion clinics! Not less.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Michael Bridge","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89960078"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T18:08:50Z","content":"Reproductive justice is about more than the legal right to choose, it's about access to affordable care close to home.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Rachel Penny","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/22679553"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T17:12:06Z","content":"Women have the right to have control over their own bodies and make choices that are safe.  There should be equal opportunity for everyone.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Muriel Stilson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89539803"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T00:27:20Z","content":"It's time New Brunswick complies with the Supreme Court ruling of 1988","like_count":0,"author_name":"Megan Stewart","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78389232"},{"created_at":"2014-03-12T01:08:45Z","content":"Abortions are a terrible thing with large social and personal costs when they are necessary, and we should work hard to limit the amount required through positive education and contraceptive accessibility...that being said, if abortion does become the best option, it damn sure should be legal and well funded. Swag.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Nicholas Kennedy","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/85364673"},{"created_at":"2014-03-13T22:45:16Z","content":"Primarily to piss off religious fundies.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Chris Blakely","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/85613611"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T16:09:45Z","content":"All women deserve the right to make decisions about their body. Patient autonomy is one of the most important things in medicine, and the lack of access to a funded abortion clinic impedes this. This is the 21st century, and availability to therapeutic abortions should be the standard of care in Canada.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Heather Stone","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/21719931"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T21:37:00Z","content":"If women don't have rights also, where is the \"equality\" ?","like_count":0,"author_name":"Tiffany Drost","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89288648"},{"created_at":"2014-04-12T00:20:05Z","content":"Every woman should have a choice to decide what is right for her and have access to safe,  affordable healthcare without being judged.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jeenifer Fox","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89417072"},{"created_at":"2014-04-20T16:31:46Z","content":"I may live in Nova Scotia, but I won't ignore it just because it's in another province.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Chantal Hawley","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/44662176"},{"created_at":"2014-03-11T21:40:06Z","content":"I have never had this happen to me, but say if it did i wouldn't be able to have a baby since i am to young with a lot of my life ahead of me. I am a college student and paying off my student loan is hard enough, it would basically be impossible for me to have a child and be able to support her/him. If this did happen to me, at least i would be able to fall back onto something.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Tina Muray","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/85346425"},{"created_at":"2014-03-24T22:24:28Z","content":"pour le libre choix de chaque femme","like_count":0,"author_name":"Gina Tremblay","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/87209225"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T12:53:05Z","content":"While I don't think that abortion should be used as a form of birth control or for correcting irresponsible sex, I do believe that women should have choices available to them at all times. There are too many factors in pregnancy to ignore abortion as a possible outcome.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Erin Daly","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89361789"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T17:11:02Z","content":"Please, please, please do not put women's needs second. We deserve to be recognized. We deserve equity. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Emily Cameron","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89258801"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T15:05:52Z","content":"Every woman should have this option....NO MATTER WHAT ANYONE ELSE THINKS OR BELIEVES!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jenn Day","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89620543"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T16:31:37Z","content":"I believe every woman should have the choice to choose what happens to her body ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Laura Hyatt","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89380945"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T17:18:12Z","content":"Pregnancy is not as simple as baby = happy family life, and women need qualified facilities like this when they decide the time is not right.","like_count":0,"author_name":"David Lipsett","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/19762069"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T17:50:46Z","content":"Abortion access is vital for women's health and wellness. Women's ability to access an abortion procedure if necessary  is something that should be taken seriously and provided through out Canada as a whole.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Samantha Rockbrune","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/38434029"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T17:07:43Z","content":"Do the right thing and repeal NB's  law so abortions are covered.  ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Elizabeth Quinlan","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/34371391"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T22:23:29Z","content":"It's embarrassing for Canada to have a province that does not consider reproductive rights to be worth supporting. This needs to change.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Joseph McGuire","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/12520058"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T22:12:31Z","content":"There are so many important women in my life, all of whom are deserving of equal rights and control over their bodies. Unfortunately for them, unwanted pregnancies can occur that can more often than not be due to a male's ignorance or selfishness. The women of this city, and of the world deserve clinics such as the Morgentaler to ensure that they retain control over their own bodies, and make their own decisions. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Alex Tracy-Gould","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/9254860"},{"created_at":"2014-04-15T18:16:03Z","content":"It's about choice.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Cyress Udell","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/53166417"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T16:13:40Z","content":"The constitutional rights of women have to be protected and the same for New Brunswick population as for the other provinces, out of the hands of provincial egoistical politicians. One minister diabetic develops a program to ease the cost of treatments for diabetics, we need further dedication to women , they are those who suffer from the lack of support in this already difficult situation. You have to put your private agenda and private thinking apart, and start respecting those who do not think like you","like_count":0,"author_name":"Chantal Trudeau","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89536160"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T01:14:15Z","content":"PRO CHOICE!!!! This Prov needs to step up to the plate, realize the importance of this clinic and its services!!  FUNDING NOW!!!!!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Laura Thurston","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89315296"},{"created_at":"2014-04-12T14:16:18Z","content":"Women should have autonomy over their body and should have the freedom of choice. Closing down abortion clinics doesn't stop abortion, it instead forces women to seek unsafe and dangerous methods since she has no choice.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jurgienne Umali","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89459743"},{"created_at":"2014-04-15T02:20:49Z","content":"Pro-choice because we can't live other people's lives.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Carol Taylor","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89689314"},{"created_at":"2014-04-12T15:57:55Z","content":"As someone who lived in New Brunswick for 4 years and would love to return someday, this horrifies me.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jennifer Berntson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/30014792"},{"created_at":"2014-04-28T18:17:48Z","content":"Women's Rights are VERY IMPORTANT!!! ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Keith Agnew","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/88812488"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T16:21:16Z","content":"It is a woman's right.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Samantha Hunt","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/71783835"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T22:03:10Z","content":"Every woman should have access to a safe abortion. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sheila Macoomb","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89292446"},{"created_at":"2014-04-12T03:16:16Z","content":"I could not imagine being forced to carry a baby I could not take care of because I dont have access to other options. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Celina Parfitt","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89426143"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T19:17:28Z","content":"Reproductive rights must be protected. Women should not be forced to seek the approval of two physicians in order to obtain a provincially funded abortion.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Elaine Simon","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89547151"},{"created_at":"2014-04-15T21:05:31Z","content":"It is outrageous that women will no longer have access to safe abortion procedures, because the province doesn't want to do their part and subsidize the procedure. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Melody Sorenson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89783588"},{"created_at":"2014-04-19T18:43:08Z","content":"Because woman should have the option to do what they want with their bodies. That option or choice shouldn't be taken away from them.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Miranda Hill","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/90191122"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T19:52:31Z","content":"Women's Rights!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Victoria Ridgley","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89273706"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T20:36:32Z","content":"It's a violation of womens rights.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Crystal Stafford","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89280108"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T19:32:38Z","content":"Women deserve the right to choose.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kalleena hunter","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/84021883"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T17:21:29Z","content":"Women should be treated with respect...not harmed by Alward's right wing beliefs","like_count":0,"author_name":"Malcolm Miller","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89634686"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T21:09:42Z","content":"Women's Rights are at stake. We are in 2014 now, we shouldn't be taking any steps backwards, especially when it comes to both the physical and mental health of a person. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Emily Quartermain","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78395556"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T21:30:21Z","content":"Reproductive righst are just that, a right.  They are not a privilege.  Everyone deserve to have access to safe, reasonable services and NB and PEI are losing that with the lose of this clinic.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Bryan Viau","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/35465508"},{"created_at":"2014-04-27T16:18:26Z","content":"My body, my choice","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lee Carter","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/16102526"},{"created_at":"2014-03-14T12:41:30Z","content":"women have the right to decide what to do with their bodies not the government and the provincial government is refusing to recognize Canadian law on this issue ","like_count":0,"author_name":"jaclyn lonsdale","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/85680734"},{"created_at":"2014-04-12T00:20:09Z","content":"An injustice for women of NB is an injustice for all women!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Myrl Eddy","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/80463279"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T02:12:34Z","content":"Regardless of your position on this issue, the option must be available to every Canadian woman to control her reproductive health. Not only this, but the option should be available to women in order to keep affected men involved in their own reproductive health and romantic/sexual relationships as well. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Charles Bourne","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/12813605"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T14:20:23Z","content":"As a nurse and mom  of three  I feel the alternative- requiring 2 docs to  \"decide\" and deem the abortion of any woman in NB in the yr 2014  disgustingly humiliating and arachaic This is not the stone age  women  have reproductive rights that are being denied in this province as it is the only one in Canada that does not fund abortions from medicare- its  a disgrace. Good luck  travelling to the 2 facilities to ask for or get  one if you pass the test- most Nb women dont have access to a family dr let alone  can arrange access to 2 to decide her life and body  choices for her.. shame on the Alward government!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jenifer Acheson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/27764612"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T16:31:41Z","content":"Are we really still living in an age in CANADA where women don't have any say in what they do with their bodies? SHAME ON THE NB GOVERNMENT FOR TAKING THAT RIGHT AWAY FROM WOMEN! What is this, red state America? BOOOOOOOOO!!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Katherine Lee","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89380952"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T21:52:47Z","content":"I am from NB and when I make my return I would like to see a change for the better and not the other way around.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Luke Carmont","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89407341"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T19:30:40Z","content":"Health care is for everyone, not those who can afford it!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Tara Audibert","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89090595"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T21:54:24Z","content":"There is way too much suffrage and trauma going on and when I hear that women in need of help are going to be turned away because they can't pay high rates as such for abortions, I am very saddened and angered. The women\u2019s movement made a ripple effect surrounding sexual reproductive rights, and it took us a very long time to receive these rights. It is clear that whoever is working at this clinic does NOT have women's rights in their best interest and that is NOT right. With abuse rates only getting higher, and as well as rates of poverty, women will have to turn to cheap and willing doctors, and there will be an even higher amount of botched procedures ending in many deaths by infection if not blood loss. Thank you so much for putting this petition in place.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Janique St-Laurent","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89671941"},{"created_at":"2014-04-16T21:51:39Z","content":"Because I I'm pro-choice!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kathleen  savoie","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/3575758"},{"created_at":"2014-04-12T16:16:38Z","content":"Everyone should have access to the health care in their prov. and the choice to decide where to have the procedure performed","like_count":0,"author_name":"Dorothy Cail","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89467137"},{"created_at":"2014-03-27T18:07:22Z","content":"Abortion is a health service that should be available to those requiring or requesting it. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Natalie Fraser","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/87584915"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T05:04:09Z","content":"Because women should be able to do whatever the fuck they want with their bodies. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Aislinn Timoon","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89451989"},{"created_at":"2014-04-15T14:53:50Z","content":"Because all Canadian women should have access to free abortions across the country. Lack of access to abortions in NB increase the medical risks of abortions.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Edith Guilbert","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89740197"},{"created_at":"2014-04-16T14:15:05Z","content":"I am a woman, and I own my own body, as does my daughter, and I want to keep it that way.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Gisele Whalen","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89883495"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T12:37:38Z","content":"NB government is breaking the law.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Tianna Gerber","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89523969"},{"created_at":"2014-04-15T17:19:31Z","content":"Women's rights must be upheld.Thank you for carrying the message to another generation of women. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Michelle Fulton","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89753194"},{"created_at":"2014-03-24T16:19:18Z","content":"Every Canadian citizen deserves equal access to health care services, regardless of the ideology of those in charge. Violating the Canada Health Act *and* ignoring the precedent set by R v Morgentaler is unconscionable.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Franki Harrogate","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/2051240"},{"created_at":"2014-03-28T01:46:47Z","content":"All women should have equal access to health care.  Abortion is a health care service. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Stacey Cline","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/87655951"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T03:24:36Z","content":"It is important to me because the right to have an abortion should be every woman's right. Women should be able to do whatever they choose with their bodies. Taking away the Morgentaler Clinic in Fredericton is a step backwards in women's rights. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Vanessa Langille","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89323979"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T10:25:37Z","content":"This is against women's reproductive rights! You're supposed to be able to get an abortion if you want to, not have to have it 'medically necessary' and I certainly couldn't afford to have it done if I wanted to","like_count":0,"author_name":"Elizabeth Gerhardt","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78380983"},{"created_at":"2014-04-15T01:42:46Z","content":"Canadian Women should be able to choose, regardless of where they love.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kim Walker","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/29858414"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T14:31:44Z","content":"Women need and deserve the right to make their own medical decisions, and also need access to safe and affordable abortion clinics! This will only create an underground market and an unsafe situation for many women. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Rachel Moore","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/61098420"},{"created_at":"2014-04-12T19:38:33Z","content":"Because women have the right to choose.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Nicole Deschenes","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89480314"},{"created_at":"2014-04-03T13:48:09Z","content":"SVP, respectez la d\u00e9cision Morgentaler de 1988","like_count":0,"author_name":"Centre des femmes du Plateau Mont-Royal","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/88340782"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T13:43:07Z","content":"People have the right to abortions!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Delilah Kingston-Grant","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89366031"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T02:20:59Z","content":"It's this kind of backwards thinking that keeps New Brunswick (and the rest of the maritimes for that matter) lagging behind the rest of the country. I am ashamed that the place I call home shows no respect for women's rights and angry that it takes an event like this to draw attention to some of the major flaws in governmental priorities NB experiences.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sarah Follett","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89500145"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T06:48:21Z","content":"This is a health issue for women and an access to health care for all not just those that can afford to travel or who live in other provinces. The ability to choose what to do with a woman's body should be a free choice for all women; regardless of where they live.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Tricia Edgar","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89508204"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T18:28:57Z","content":"Abortion is a right. Stop the terrible things that happen when access to safe and legal abortions is denied. Please.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Linda Bolton","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/29862222"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T22:30:59Z","content":"I am ashamed that the province I grew up in still denies women easy access to free and safe legal abortions. There are a lot of reasons why a woman might choose to end a pregnancy and both doctors and the government should not hold jurisdiction over this choice and appropriate access to health care.","like_count":0,"author_name":"C.J. Rowe","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/3111350"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T19:25:08Z","content":"Women have the right to have a choice. These medical services should be available to whoever needs them!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Chelsey LeBlanc","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89547593"},{"created_at":"2014-04-15T02:28:24Z","content":"Because I have two daughters and one grand-daughter.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Gary Williams","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89689735"},{"created_at":"2014-03-10T15:59:15Z","content":"Women without their own family doctors (especially when we have such a shortage) are unable to get a proper referral and are left having to pay for their procedure only because of the short-comings of the NB healthcare system. On top of that the lingering stigma of abortions lead many women to avoid consulting their primary healthcare provider, leaving them to pay for something they shouldn't have to (we do pay taxes after all and have universal health care) to keep the procedure more secretive. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jannike Smith","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/54713480"},{"created_at":"2014-04-12T23:56:02Z","content":"women have a right to choose what they do with there body. People get into situations and sometimes need a little help. What kind of difference does it  make to your life? Why are you so concerned about something like that when there are kids around the world homeless and starving and being abused already why don't we fix those problems first. Instead of making this an issue, when its not.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Emma Pirie","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89494604"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T11:36:05Z","content":" Women and children, victims of incest, rape and other crimes of violence must not be punished all their lives while a perpetrator  goes realtively free.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Elizabeth McLaughlin","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/6636660"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T17:56:46Z","content":"I am a Family Doctor and it is not fair for patients in PEI and New Brunswick to have such a hard time getting access to abortion services. This private clinic is a big help as access to these services is already very difficult in the province. For the clinic to shut down would be a total disaster and a slap in the face for the rights of our women and patients. Not only should this clinic stay open, but the services should also be government funded. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Saneea Abboud","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89639805"},{"created_at":"2014-04-17T13:08:55Z","content":"A woman has the right to choose to terminate an unwanted pregnancy.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jennifer Shirley","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/23016865"},{"created_at":"2014-04-29T22:12:09Z","content":"Freedom of choice for women is key to the improvement of life and well being for women and children, as well as all other members of Canadian society. The beliefs of some, must not and can not, over ride the personal rights of others to make their own choices.","like_count":0,"author_name":"M Chorney","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/74748153"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T23:23:16Z","content":"I could not be more disgusted in my home province. This issue has brought to light the whole other can of worms concerning the availability of abortions for women.  The provincial government needs to help fund and make services easier for women who need them. The current standards are abysmal and archaic.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Brent Gladney","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/3599205"},{"created_at":"2014-03-10T01:45:43Z","content":"Because some people make mistakes, and others aren't fit to be parents , whether they be teens or trailer trash...","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jackson Pearson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/85122688"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T21:01:49Z","content":"Government should not be able to control our lives. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Justin Smith-Wilson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89666993"},{"created_at":"2014-04-12T15:58:04Z","content":"My mother had an abortion before it was legal or safe and the trauma of it left her devastated for life. Women deserve access to safe, legal abortions. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Hilary Prue","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89465907"},{"created_at":"2014-04-16T03:54:06Z","content":"Access to safe, FREE abortion is a LEGAL RIGHT in Canada. It is unconscionable that women in New Brunswick don't have access to this vital health service.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sarah  Lebel","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/21218489"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T15:11:13Z","content":"because our province is already messed up enough financially , last thing we need is hundreds more babies on welfare. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"sean MacCallum","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/56910028"},{"created_at":"2014-03-10T16:06:41Z","content":"I believe in the right to choose. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Fergus Baird","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/26263119"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T15:02:22Z","content":"Not everyone has assess to family doctor's and health care. For those that do, they can be met with opposition and judgement. This is  difficult enough for that individual, the present system can be unfair and unbearable.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Cynthia Davis","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89620156"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T19:01:23Z","content":"The fact that the provinces of NB and PEI do not fund abortions in the year 2014 astounds me. This needs to change.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Tom Ogden","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/2641561"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T19:49:25Z","content":"Laissons le libre choix \u00e0 la femme.  Nous sommes en 2014. Comment \u00e7a se fait qu'une femme ne peut prendre la d\u00e9cision seule.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sylvie Provencher","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89273267"},{"created_at":"2014-04-16T14:34:00Z","content":"Uphold section 7 of the Charter. Uphold the SCC's decision in Morgentaler, and now Chaoulli (Chaoulli v Quebec (Attorney General), 2005 SCC 35). If you do this, you can guarantee a lawsuit will be coming your way, with precedent that is not in your favour. Do it for the 1/4 women that you know and love who have been sexually assaulted and have had to contemplate this decision (even if they did not conceive). Let them know that no matter what happens, they will have that choice. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Julie DeWolf","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/11682845"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T18:23:27Z","content":"The Morgentaler Clinic serves as a safe purpose for many, I have always been pro choice and I believe if there is a place that can help with addressing the issues of abortions more safely. No one should condemn the right to foreclose it, but instead support it. Please do not close this Clinic. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Katherine Bennett","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89643499"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T22:57:07Z","content":"Every women should have a choice, lets not go back to the days of butchering .","like_count":0,"author_name":"Leila Baxter","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/68417717"},{"created_at":"2014-04-16T16:27:06Z","content":"All women have the right to decided when and if they become parents.  It is NOT the role of government to obstruct that decision.  Medical access to therapeutic abortion is a necessary part of maternal health in Canada.  STOP PLAYING WITH WOMEN'S LIVES!!! ","like_count":0,"author_name":"S McEwing","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/545704"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T19:50:36Z","content":"Reproductive rights are human rights, and should not be dissected, maligned, and considered negotiable.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Theresa Lee","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89656235"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T19:09:41Z","content":"Your government's unwillingness to fund abortions in NB will now result in women having to travel out of province to receive this procedure. With so many people already leaving the province in search of better opportunities, do you really want to provide the population with yet another reason to look out of province? Further, not all women have the means to travel out of province to receive this procedure. Do you really want to encourage women to take unsafe alternatives to terminate a pregnancy due to lack of options? As a former NB resident who left as soon as I graduated from university, I am appalled that you do not respect women's reproductive rights. As an economically stagnant province, perhaps you should consider empowering female residents and providing them with options. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jennifer Bleakney","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36339749"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T14:59:32Z","content":"At this risk of sounding heartless, the world does not need more babies, especially unwanted ones.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Michael Rooney","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/3591690"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T00:43:41Z","content":"This is not an issue that should be up for debate. This is an issue of human rights in which case women are being discriminated and denied the opportunity to express this essential human right. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"elizabeth kent","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89496590"},{"created_at":"2014-04-15T16:52:44Z","content":"Nobody has the right to take away women's choice, not even god, because s/he gave it to humans in the first place","like_count":0,"author_name":"Ashley DeMartini","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89750023"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T22:12:37Z","content":"This is my home town and having these rights taken away devastates me.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sydney de Jonge","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89293898"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T18:08:11Z","content":"Women have the right to free, easily accessible, and safe abortions.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Tania Chandler","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/60008050"},{"created_at":"2014-04-28T23:50:36Z","content":"Women have the right to make decisions about their lives ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kathy Vansickle","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/7475035"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T21:12:21Z","content":"To keep women safe and allowing choice.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Bliss Roberts","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/67858813"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T23:23:24Z","content":"Bodily autonomy, the right to have personal choice over how a citizen's own body is used, is a crucial human right. By refusing women this, not only do you make them second class citizens, but third class citizens who must sacrifice their agency for a hypothetical future society member. You provide women with less rights to self than a corpse, which is protected from interference even in death. Absolutely reprehensible.  ","like_count":0,"author_name":"K. Attwell","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/2933211"},{"created_at":"2014-04-12T13:43:43Z","content":"The decision to have a medically covered abortion should be an individual choice for every woman faced with an unwanted pregnancy with her doctor in attendance. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Heather Clements","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89457826"},{"created_at":"2014-04-16T13:04:08Z","content":"It is important because it violates a decision made by a higher court. If governments feel they have the power to igno