r regular healthcare. Abortion is a personal choice and should be allowed, except for as a method of contraception, in my opinion. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Isabel Baltzan","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/29555107"},{"created_at":"2014-04-15T03:21:44Z","content":"Everyone should have the right to choose. It's their body/their life. A medical reason shouldn't be the only reason to allow an abortion. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Krista Parker","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89692537"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T15:04:48Z","content":"I required this vital service in the past and it is the most basic reproductive right of women and men to safely terminate pregnancies that would inevitably result in disastrous lives for all involved. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"John Nolan","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89373521"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T16:57:55Z","content":"The right to autonomy and safety of one's person are basic human rights. By refusing to fund abortion for women who are ending their pregnancy by choice (rather than \"medical necessity\" - at best a subjective factor), the province of New Brunswick is effectively endangering the lives of all women in the province and refusing them their human rights. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jen Dube","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/12680320"},{"created_at":"2014-03-12T15:20:39Z","content":"No women should be deterred from making autonomous decisions about their own body.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Gabriela Rozanski","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/85427228"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T20:19:17Z","content":"L'avortement est un DROIT fondamental qui permet aux femmes \u00e0 disposer de leur corps.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Val\u00e9rie Poitras","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/68135397"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T23:26:08Z","content":"It's a woman's choice and right.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jayceon Terrell Taylor","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/47195274"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T22:58:39Z","content":"Because babies shouldn't be brought into the world to people who don't want them","like_count":0,"author_name":"Amanda Lutes","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89301737"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T01:14:40Z","content":"Because I am a woman.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kari Kruse","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/58574852"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T04:01:15Z","content":"The NB government should be ashamed of themselves. This is discrimination against women and disgusts me!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Victoria West","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89326077"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T12:31:24Z","content":"Because I am pro-choice.  I believe that all people have the right to say what happens to their bodies, male or female, and with this clinic closing, it is showing everyone that the province does not believe that we have that choice.  ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Norma Prianti","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/51529656"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T22:01:20Z","content":"What an embarrassing step backwards for New Brunswick. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Hilary Burt","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89407909"},{"created_at":"2014-04-06T01:45:03Z","content":"Women need true choice.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Diana Nuttall","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/49555734"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T14:35:46Z","content":"Having a choice is everyone's right.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Melodi Rosario-Hachey","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89370852"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T18:48:08Z","content":"ALL WOMEN should have safe, rapid and accessible access to abortion.  Not just when other people tell her it's \"medically necessary\"","like_count":0,"author_name":"Annie  Morrison","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/10590885"},{"created_at":"2014-03-09T20:31:56Z","content":"Every woman should have a choice. It was ruled not to be a criminal choice long ago, why has it taken so long? It is time trust women when deciding on her reproductive health ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Chantal Harris","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/85101131"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T21:30:10Z","content":"Women need this. The right of choice.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sherry McCoy","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89287741"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T23:34:14Z","content":"women deserve this choice...when u are  a young girl and u still have a life ahead of you.. and things happen..well u need the option...mistakes are part of life...there are too many unwanted children in this world...80% at least....are in proverty..no way to life life for them.","like_count":0,"author_name":"jeannette bezanson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89414276"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T04:14:07Z","content":"This is so important to me because everyone should have the right to make their own choices without anyone forcing their own morality upon them. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Mike Brace","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89195219"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T23:21:01Z","content":"It's not important to me but right now there are a lot of females that need this place to exist for personal reasons and I'd hate to see them left with nowhere to turn. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Morgan Harn","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89306042"},{"created_at":"2014-03-10T04:14:47Z","content":"Time to catch up to other provinces! ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lindsi George","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/24585634"},{"created_at":"2014-04-15T17:54:54Z","content":"Women's right to choose should be recognize as a human right. Abortion is legal in Canada and it's not a real choice if you don't have access to abortion services wether it's because it costs way too much, you have to travel very far to get it, etc.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Evelyne Morrissette","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/44965806"},{"created_at":"2014-03-10T01:37:17Z","content":"I believe that all women should have the right to choice in whatever they do, and their reproductive rights are no one's business but their own and no one else should have power over them in that way.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Hannah Stockford","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36175024"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T23:58:05Z","content":" Time for NB to get in line with the rest of Canada. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Davina McFarlane","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89309926"},{"created_at":"2014-03-10T04:14:48Z","content":"Time to catch up to other provinces! ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lindsi George","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/24585634"},{"created_at":"2014-04-12T10:52:28Z","content":"Every woman has the right to safe abortion, this should NOT be taken away!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Brandon Hachey","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/61802581"},{"created_at":"2014-04-20T16:41:29Z","content":"The safety of women matters, this whole issue shows us that our government doesn't agree that women need the same rights as men, but that (due to our anatomies) those rights are displayed differently.  ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jenny Tremblay","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/90239807"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T01:40:46Z","content":"Why is this important to me? Any time humans are denied basic human rights it's important to me. Women MUST have the choice to abort, and without this clinic, they won't have that choice.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Rodney DuPlessis","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89317092"},{"created_at":"2014-04-15T00:24:00Z","content":"Women should be able to choose whether or not they keep a child. It's ridiculous to think that they don't even get a chance to choose.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Courtney Berthelot","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/85301610"},{"created_at":"2014-04-16T09:31:42Z","content":"This issue is important to me because it is my right as a woman, and as a woman I am concerned for the future of women's rights in Canada. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Shauna Robar","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89855737"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T12:55:50Z","content":"New Brunswick Regulation 84-20, which requires women to get referrals from 2 physicians and have their abortion done by a specialist in a hospital, is nearly identical to s.251 of the Criminal Code of Canada, which was struck down by the Supreme Court in 1988 (Morgentaler v R). There is not a single US state, despite their restrictions on abortions, that require 2 doctor referral to a specialist for a first trimester abortion. This is a non-partisan issue, as successive Progressive Conservative government in Alberta have funded services at the Morgentaler Clinic in Edmonton. In other words, nowhere in North America, but New Brunswick is there this kind of restriction on access to medically safe abortions. Every province in this country funds clinic visits through our universal single-payer healthcare systems, except New Brunswick.\r\n\r\nIt's time for David Alward's government to comply with the Supreme Court ruling in Morgentaler v R (1988) and strike Regulation 84-20 from the books. Every abortion is a medically necessary abortion. The decision should not be taken from the woman, whose body is being used against her wishes, and put into the hands of a panel of doctors, whose new patient waitlist is more than 3 years long in this province. People deserve safe access to decide and plan their reproductive futures for themselves. It is unconscionable that the state would try to take that decision-making process away from them.\r\n\r\nI call on the New Brunswick government to end Regulation 84-20 and, like all other provinces, fund patient visits to Morgentaler Clinics, in compliance with the Canada Health Act and the Morgentaler v R (1988)  Supreme Court of Canada decision.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jim Dunbar","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/11312455"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T16:26:42Z","content":"I am a human being, and I should have basic rights to my own body.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Emilie Turner","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89380530"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T18:23:49Z","content":"For the safety and human rights of women.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Karah Gri","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/71796479"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T19:15:39Z","content":"Because it's my right.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Renee Hebert","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89395105"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T20:15:43Z","content":"There are a lot of unwanted children in this world if someone knows they are unfit to be a parent why force them into something they are not ready for","like_count":0,"author_name":"Nadege Levrier","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89400051"},{"created_at":"2014-03-11T19:03:20Z","content":"Free and safe access to abortion should available to all women.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Anna Hartley","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/85325206"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T22:06:44Z","content":"I believe in the right of choice.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jasmine Bell","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89292993"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T15:32:51Z","content":"Come on Mr. Alward do something positive for NB!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Ronald Phillips","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89533830"},{"created_at":"2014-03-11T01:07:24Z","content":"Rights to do why I want with my body. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"sophie stimac","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/85236881"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T02:59:16Z","content":"Woman should have the right to have an abortion if they choose so.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Brandon Schaus","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/23771415"},{"created_at":"2014-03-10T09:21:39Z","content":"Because every women has a right to their own body, a right to live their life","like_count":0,"author_name":"Timothy Maloney","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/85142557"},{"created_at":"2014-04-15T02:05:53Z","content":"I'm a human being who cares about other human beings, also a native New Brunswicker","like_count":0,"author_name":"Mary MacLean","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/15134200"},{"created_at":"2014-03-12T10:41:15Z","content":"Health care is a right. So is a woman's choice. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"John Arthur Bell","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/9196255"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T21:54:08Z","content":"Access to safe and affordable healthcare is essential.  Our province should be ashamed of not improving access to women's' health services (abortion in particular) sooner.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Katelyn Kent","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/47299788"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T01:35:28Z","content":"I am from Fredericton, New Brunswick, and feel that this is an important issue to take care of. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Danielle Leger","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/70037571"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T22:16:00Z","content":"Equality","like_count":0,"author_name":"Bernadine Joel","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89408823"},{"created_at":"2014-04-15T18:34:03Z","content":"Suite \u00e0 la fermeture de la clinique Morgentaler, un grand nombre de femmes du Nouveau-Brunswick \u2013 surtout les femmes d\u00e9j\u00e0 marginalis\u00e9es et vivant en pauvret\u00e9 - ne seront plus en mesure d\u2019acc\u00e9der \u00e0 des services d\u2019interruption volontaire ou m\u00e9dicale d\u2019une grossesse.  Toutes les femmes doivent avoir le droit \u00e0 l'accessibilit\u00e9, la gratuit\u00e9 et le libre-choix en mati\u00e8re d'avortement.  ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Suzanne Bouclin","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/23904975"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T20:15:49Z","content":"Because I don't think my rights should be dictated by the government.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Marcia Nyeste","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89550595"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T01:31:47Z","content":"It's the only place for women to GET abortions in the MARITIMES! Women have a right to their own bodies, and for their reproductive health! If this closes, women WILL resort to other means, they won't just have the baby. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Tayla MacDonald","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89498384"},{"created_at":"2014-03-10T18:21:29Z","content":"Women's right to make their own choices","like_count":0,"author_name":"Nadine Edwards","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/85189743"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T20:10:52Z","content":"It's been more than 20 years since Canada's Supreme Court determined that a woman's right to choose was a fundamental right in this country. To see the New Brunswick government not take the necessary initiatives to ensure the rights of women of this province are adequately protected is both angering and sad.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Karla O'Regan","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/23725751"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T22:44:50Z","content":"This is a women's right issue. We deserve access to the facilities necessary for us to have an abortion","like_count":0,"author_name":"Emily Blue","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89298966"},{"created_at":"2014-04-12T15:45:49Z","content":"Women should have the right to make decisions about their bodies, and should have the right to terminate an unwanted pregnancy. This is supposed to be the age of equality, not the age of oppression. Closing a clinic will not stop abortions, just make them more dangerous and cause more deaths in those who cannot afford to shell out the cash to abort their pregnancy in Montreal.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Alora Reid","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/11124217"},{"created_at":"2014-03-10T13:35:19Z","content":"Pro-Choice","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jordan Hodgin","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/85162400"},{"created_at":"2014-04-12T19:50:04Z","content":"As a Canadian woman, I feel tremendous solidarity for the women of Martimes.  I hope that they will always have their bodily autonomy respected so that they can be safe and happy.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Colleen Metcalf","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89481369"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T11:33:04Z","content":"This service needs to be available to teenage girls and women of all ages.","like_count":0,"author_name":"andrew buszchak","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89611851"},{"created_at":"2014-04-12T23:47:21Z","content":"Religious thinking and lack of support will not take away my rights as a woman","like_count":0,"author_name":"Tatiana Collette","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89494215"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T19:51:00Z","content":"An abortion is already a time of emotional and physical stress. Creating barriers to seek this procedure is a backward measure that puts all women in the surrounding area at risk, and quite frankly infringes on their rights as Canadian citizens. Ensure the clinic remains open so New Brunswick women have safe access to a place that allows them to exercise their reproductive rights, and FUND the clinic so that one of the most impoverished areas of Canada isn't the one being forced to pay out of pocket to keep a centre of health open!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Amber Robinson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/8504752"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T19:12:28Z","content":"Women should have the right to choose! It should no longer be a political debate. If people are against abortion then they should use empirical evidence and support poverty-reduction strategies and funding increases for single parents.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Rob Moir","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89546739"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T03:25:22Z","content":"Every child a wanted child. Choice is for life!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Victoria Lehman","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/2535259"},{"created_at":"2014-03-12T02:07:46Z","content":"Personal experience. Everyone deserves the choice.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jael Henri","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/56740204"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T13:49:11Z","content":"I want to have to right over my own body. If this right is not given to women, they will take up upon themselves to terminate their own pregnancies--women are going to die. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"celine b","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/20003522"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T14:35:54Z","content":"Save the Morgentaler Clinic now! ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Diana Massot","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/14878755"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T16:32:13Z","content":"Every woman should have the opportunity to do what they want with their bodies in a safe space, and if the government isn't willing to support women's heath needs, then the government needs to change.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Cat McCluskey","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/17138110"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T16:42:14Z","content":"Women's reproductive rights are just that. Funding should NOT be a question here. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Julia  Rose","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/2501237"},{"created_at":"2014-04-29T16:52:23Z","content":"Because it's my body not yours.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Tess Aguinaga","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/91136267"},{"created_at":"2014-04-09T23:16:52Z","content":"It is unacceptable that the province of New Brunswick does not fund abortion services. Safe, professional abortion services should be accessible to all women, for any reason, free of cost, and the decision regarding abortion should rest with the woman, not healthcare providers. Funding abortion services would enhance women's reproductive rights in this province and ensure that no unsafe or self-abortions happen, which can be very dangerous for women. I urge the New Brunswick government to look across the country and see that these services are being funded by other provincial governments, so why is New Brunswick so behind on this issue and why is it failing to serve the women of our province so profoundly?","like_count":0,"author_name":"Emily Leaman","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89173798"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T14:02:45Z","content":"Human rights .","like_count":0,"author_name":"Brent Walsh","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89528864"},{"created_at":"2014-03-24T15:24:15Z","content":"When abortion can not be made safely, women dye from secondary effects of home made abortions!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Nesrine Bessaih","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/39332326"},{"created_at":"2014-03-14T15:33:53Z","content":"I believe in the freedom to choose.  Having a child is not a small task, its a HUGE decision with many different facets to consider not just medical. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lauren Murdock","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/85703376"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T22:06:30Z","content":"Every child needs/deserves to be truly wanted, loved and cared for. Our nation needs/ deserves the same.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Janet Shively","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/47142063"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T16:26:47Z","content":"Lives and rights of Canadian women must be protected !","like_count":0,"author_name":"Serena Laskin","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/20674417"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T22:39:15Z","content":"Women are entitled to the right to decide what to do with their bodies. Without the clinic, the process required to have an abortion becomes much more tedious, and the lack of facilities in which the procedure can be carried out and the limited number of abortion patients the hospital in Moncton can accept each day, keeping in mind that the majority of the women in the province would have to go there for their procedure, hugely restricts the accessibility of such procedures.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jeff Retallick","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/21990390"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T22:47:29Z","content":"it is essential for all women to have control over their own bodies, and to have access to this type of service when they need it, not when two other people say she needs it.   And to have this service available at a location where it is not priced out of her reach.  ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sharon Hicks","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/80203455"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T20:49:20Z","content":"Because women absolutely need access to clinics like this or risk their own lives elsewhere.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Mackenzie Smith","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89552481"},{"created_at":"2014-04-12T12:05:12Z","content":"A country that violates its own law is not the place I want to live in.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Valentina Capurri","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/21065035"},{"created_at":"2014-04-15T03:12:06Z","content":"There should be funded clinics all across Canada for abortion. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Ingrid Johnson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89692045"},{"created_at":"2014-03-11T14:33:23Z","content":"Access to services for women's health should be paid for by the government","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sarah-Jane Thiessen","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/52552909"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T18:54:33Z","content":"Women every where deserve the choice! ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Catrina Bourque","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89545801"},{"created_at":"2014-04-15T01:29:54Z","content":"it is important that every single woman have access, affordable and high standard of care when they choose to obtain an abortion. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Leanne P","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89686109"},{"created_at":"2014-03-10T16:18:53Z","content":"Women should have a safe choice. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Nicole Vair","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/85173388"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T14:26:03Z","content":"Everyone has the right to freedom of choice.","like_count":0,"author_name":"monica wicks","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89369954"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T15:23:30Z","content":"Every woman has the right to, or not to.....  DO NOT RESTRICT MY RIGHTS to make the proper decision while you squander my tax dollars to make your pockets fatter and deny me.  This is my tax dollars !!! Never forget WHO you work for...","like_count":0,"author_name":"Nicole Charette","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89043652"},{"created_at":"2014-03-10T18:05:58Z","content":"It should be important to everyone!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jennifer Stokes","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78014163"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T21:13:29Z","content":"I believe every woman is entitled to make decisions regarding her own body. A lack of funding is hindering a woman's ability to access fundamental healthcare!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kelsey Murrin","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89285883"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T22:31:17Z","content":"This isn't just an issue for me. This is an issue that is important for all genders. We deserve a clinic in our city and it's important to allow people the  option even if you're for or against.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Robbie Rowinski","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89296699"},{"created_at":"2014-04-28T22:52:31Z","content":"freedom of choice is a fundamental human right.  Access to safe abortions is fundamental to a safe and healthy future for all.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jennifer Davis","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/91054568"},{"created_at":"2014-04-15T01:57:51Z","content":"People should have the right to make choices for them, their body and their mind. There are many stories out there, Too young, rape, etc. These otions should be there  for people in turmoil, whatever reason it is. I am afraid that they will turn to backroom \"doctors\" or worse, sucide because they have no options. No , I don't think it should be closed. It should be kept.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Wendy Kinney","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/22823668"},{"created_at":"2014-03-25T05:23:08Z","content":"This violates the Morgentaler Supreme Court decision of 1988, which ruled that restrictions like these are unconstitutional because they violate women\u2019s rights. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Marg Bizuk","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/87234006"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T14:46:25Z","content":"because its 2014","like_count":0,"author_name":"victoria jewett","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89371791"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T17:54:20Z","content":"I'm grateful and fortunate that this clinic was accessible in my time of need three summers ago. Many women lack family doctors, will be refused referrals for abortions by doctors with \"moral objections,\" or simply cannot travel to Moncton for abortion services.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Emily Merrithew","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/48005031"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T16:01:30Z","content":"Control over one's body is a recognized human right.  Every child a wanted child!","like_count":0,"author_name":"J'Nan Brown","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89378437"},{"created_at":"2014-03-16T01:06:07Z","content":"New Brunswick is voilating decisions of the Supreme Court and the Canada Health Act? Obey them now before spending tax dollars on a court debacle!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jennifer Stotland","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/12053984"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T21:26:01Z","content":"I'm a woman. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Molly Strickland","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/8180735"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T21:50:46Z","content":"women's rights! ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Michaela D'Intino","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/7511017"},{"created_at":"2014-03-11T21:40:47Z","content":"Because it is the right thing to do.","like_count":0,"author_name":"M. L. Taylor","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/47009114"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T23:44:47Z","content":"I'm a woman. Everyone deserves this right. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Anna  Farrell","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/5025148"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T14:23:46Z","content":"People have the right to make their own choices about their reproductive health!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Julie Michaud","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/2640403"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T06:25:23Z","content":"Let's take women's health seriously!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Leslie Bragg","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89595870"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T15:28:05Z","content":"I support the reproductive choice of all women. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Barb Fornssler","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/15143636"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T18:35:12Z","content":"As a Women and a Mother. And also someone who has used a service like this it is our right. To chose what we do with our body it should not be up to anyone else to make our decisons or force more children to. Born when therei another option","like_count":0,"author_name":"sarah larsen","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/87142011"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T20:03:13Z","content":"Following high school, my best friend since elementary school moved to New Brunswick to attend UNB Fredericton. After becoming involved with a boy, she ended up getting pregnant at the age of 18.  After countless phone calls, texts and emails, we figured the best choice for her and her future would be to get an abortion.  The wait times in Nova Scotia were too long to travel here to have the procedure done, so she decided it would be best to have it done at the Morgentaler abortion clinic in Fredericton. Although it was not impossible to get it done elsewhere, it was convenient and without a doubt, essential in her life at that time.  There are many young girls all over Canada becoming pregnant and are unable to safely raise a child which is why I would like to see this clinic stay open for other girls and women with a crisis. This issue hits home for me, and I would really like to see government funding to the Morgentaler abortion clinic.","like_count":0,"author_name":"sarah marando","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/28870690"},{"created_at":"2014-04-12T02:48:34Z","content":"No woman should have to give birth , endangering her physical or mental health, no one should impose  a restriction due to ones inability to afford the services.  The savings of legal , adoption , psychologist and medical fees  in the long term will balance out the cost of abortion . would you force your daughter to have a sick , deformed , unwanted , child or a child caused by a rape . the mental trauma the mother and child will experience May cost us more money down the road , not to mention the hardship suffered during a pregnancy. some mother health could be in jeopardy. epilepsy. Seizure is a danger due to variousness medical condition even in a healthy pregnancy , but what RISk factors do we not know. please take the time to think and consider the consequences! ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lorena Finn","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/77756594"},{"created_at":"2014-03-14T15:56:30Z","content":"Basic human rights. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Patricia West","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/74966440"},{"created_at":"2014-03-23T21:19:04Z","content":"Women's rights is important to me. Women should have a right to chose what they want to do with their bodies.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Ariane Flamain","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/45823252"},{"created_at":"2014-04-16T20:59:44Z","content":"GIRL POWER!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Mary Sohn","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89927790"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T04:24:51Z","content":"the right to choose is important","like_count":0,"author_name":"Anne Fredette","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/12154685"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T15:00:09Z","content":"because I deserve basic human rights","like_count":0,"author_name":"eleanor beale","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/45785592"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T17:35:25Z","content":"Because it is important to everyone.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Julian Merlin","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89386357"},{"created_at":"2014-03-24T13:37:28Z","content":"Woman'own decision","like_count":0,"author_name":"Claire Paiement","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/87152309"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T22:00:34Z","content":"Every woman should have the chance to make a choice, and to make that choice safely.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Katie Bull","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89292035"},{"created_at":"2014-04-12T04:23:21Z","content":"women have the right to choose!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Am\u00e9lie Parenteau-Comfort","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/41429921"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T00:51:19Z","content":"Let's not go back in time, women need help and support not discrimination and oppression. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Cindy Tulk","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/56932963"},{"created_at":"2014-03-26T14:16:54Z","content":"Get with the times, New Brunswick!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Caitlin Barry","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/87426745"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T00:26:50Z","content":"i think woman should always have a option. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Samara Murphy","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89562276"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T04:38:28Z","content":"The government needs to provide women with safe and accessible health care and options.  This is an issue of women's rights.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Chelsey Brussard","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89328248"},{"created_at":"2014-04-12T12:56:41Z","content":"It's the law!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Mark Butler","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/58327299"},{"created_at":"2014-05-05T17:26:16Z","content":"It is fundamental to justice and respect for women - to have services that provide them with reproductive choices.  Governments need to enable openness and choice in a free society.  This is not about religion it is about justice","like_count":0,"author_name":"Susan Russell","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/29901865"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T20:11:00Z","content":"Because I am a woman and this is important to uphold the freedom and rights of every woman. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sarah Walker","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/42624616"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T19:21:50Z","content":"Women need a safe place to access abortion services. Choice is a matter of utmost importance to all women in Canada. New Brunswick women should not be exempt.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Chris Chevalier","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/684250"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T02:32:56Z","content":"It is long past the time that something as simple as a woman's right to the ownership and health of her own body is debated. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Allison Holder","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89320511"},{"created_at":"2014-03-12T00:03:54Z","content":"Reproductive rights are a basic human right. NB's stance on this issue is an embarrassment and indicates a fundamental lack of respect for women's rights in this province.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Nancy Pipes","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/12896212"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T02:04:16Z","content":"It is unacceptable for NB/PEI women to have no access to these resources! We must save it. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Madison Cawker","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/2012687"},{"created_at":"2014-03-11T11:51:00Z","content":"free choice to women ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Nicole Mallet","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/41116449"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T14:26:07Z","content":"Because its a right for each womam on this earth","like_count":0,"author_name":"Alexandre Phaneuf","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89369962"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T12:47:54Z","content":"New Brunswick is underserved in every possible way. It has the highest teen pregnancy rate (or one of the highest) of any province in the country. This clinic needs public subsidies because women and girls deserve the right to choose regardless of their economic class. This is not negotiable. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jordan Arseneault","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/3495269"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T15:55:18Z","content":"All women should have control over their bodies.  Sexual assault, degradation, molestation, objectification are rampant in our society.  Women are held responsible for children, and yet not give the economic, physical or social power that that responsiblity requires, whereas men get off scott-free.  Reproductive rights, the right to control what happens to one's body, show respect to women, and free access to abortion is part of reproductive rights.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Vallie Stearns","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/84359108"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T20:30:45Z","content":"Women deserve the right.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Molly Davidson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89279285"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T18:17:33Z","content":"We already know what happens to women when abortion isn't an available option. Let's keep moving forward with women's rights, not backwards.  ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Mya Rinzler","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/32617034"},{"created_at":"2014-04-17T14:32:44Z","content":"Women have the right to make their own decisions about their body and their futures.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Christy Dingee","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/3620041"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T23:47:58Z","content":"I'm a dude, but I believe every women should have the right to choose what she does with her body and her life, removing the option to have a safe abortion is NOT okay.","like_count":0,"author_name":"andrew grattan","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/88733555"},{"created_at":"2014-04-18T22:48:33Z","content":"I believe every woman has the right to choose.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sarah Trainor","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/61755446"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T22:59:53Z","content":"It would be nice to live in a province that actually enforced Canadian law.","like_count":0,"author_name":"William Hughes","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89676593"},{"created_at":"2014-04-15T00:59:00Z","content":"Women deserve the choice. Abortions will happen either way so please give women the proper facility to have a safe procedure!!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Taylor Gillies","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89684367"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T00:35:05Z","content":"I lived in New Brunswick all my life and to see this happen sickens me. It's unacceptable to  me that they want to take women back to the dark ages and that they're comfortable leaving women without a safe alternative to their \"Panels\" decision. My body my choice!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Krista-Leah Goguen","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/58968780"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T01:03:29Z","content":"Take religion out and moral standards and give women their bodies back....there are so many reason that an abortion may be the only option...don't take that away from women and their doctors","like_count":0,"author_name":"Pauline Collette","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/43645668"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T19:26:02Z","content":"This is when women are still treated as second class citizens.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Nicole Chartrand","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89547654"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T23:24:07Z","content":"Because I'm a woman.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kathy Kattenburg","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/12909425"},{"created_at":"2014-04-19T18:10:43Z","content":"This isn't ultimately about the act of abortion, this is about women's rights.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Janessa Culleton","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/44494998"},{"created_at":"2014-03-12T14:24:13Z","content":"Why are the rights for a woman important to me? Because woman are human beings. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jennifer Nagel","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/74692519"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T15:44:54Z","content":"I've had two abortions in my life, one at 17 almost immediately after  the biggest tragedy to ever hit our town occurred during my graduating year, and one at 19 immediately following an abusive relationship with an alcoholic man. In both cases I was given a hospital procedure from an OBGYN and I was under the impression the procedure was available for free to all women. To find out after all this time that I was given two procedures with no hesitation from the doctors is something that irks me, because I've realized it was never my choice, it was up to those doctors. To realize that they decided for me is actually very upsetting in a strange way and I want to remove that power from the doctors hands. It is not for another person to ever decide. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Ashley Clowes","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/11897679"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T21:34:20Z","content":"I believe women have the right to choose. I do not want to see over population, suffering children go from foster home to foster home or in over crowded adoption shelters. I believe it's a woman's right to choose.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Angela Gray","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/84677676"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T02:30:13Z","content":"I am a women. I believe in human rights and the province of New-Brunswick should be really careful with those issues. We are already behind on this question, compared to other provinces in Canada. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Marie-Pier Albert","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89188598"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T16:14:50Z","content":"Reproductive rights are a human right.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Mackenzie Rhyason","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/72850887"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T23:48:04Z","content":"All women should have the right to choose.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Allison Whately-Doucet","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/2629191"},{"created_at":"2014-04-12T05:10:34Z","content":"Regardless of anyone's views or beliefs, the supreme court has ruled that women should have access to this procedure with ZERO stipulations. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kyle McKay","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89431024"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T02:19:28Z","content":"Every pregnancy should be a wanted pregnancy. No woman should be forced to carry a child to term that she didn't want. Universal access to medically safe abortion (NOT medically necessary abortion) should be something that every woman has access to. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Michaela Brophy","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89581899"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T11:31:44Z","content":"Women need a safe option of choice. The rates of abortion are dropping annually which means education and birth control are increasing. However we still need to make the service available for those who need it. It is a basic human right for safe care.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jim Middleton","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/84928862"},{"created_at":"2014-04-05T02:50:24Z","content":"I strongly support women's rights, including the right to choose, no matter what socio-economic status they may fall under.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kimberly Newton","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/88539766"},{"created_at":"2014-03-25T03:14:30Z","content":"Women has rights ! If 26 years ago, the Morgentaler Supreme Court decision said that type of regulation is unconstitutional, we must respect that !","like_count":0,"author_name":"Alexandre Michaud","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/27185195"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T13:00:00Z","content":"This is a basic human right for choice. Please don't let the women of New Brunswick suffer because of funding. Such an important cause for so many  that have no other option.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Elizabeth Shaw","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89362329"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T16:16:47Z","content":"It's a woman's right to choose what happens to her body and to take this option away from women, especially those financially unable, will be left without options. If the province truly cared for it's citizens then it would step in and take action to save this.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Andrew Mahaffy","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89254929"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T14:51:05Z","content":" As a woman, I have a right to decide what I wish to do with my body. It is not the choice of two doctors deeming it \"medically necessary\", it is MY body and MY choice. Women in New Brunswick and PEI have benefited from the clinic since it's opening in 1994. Without safe, legal and non-discriminatory access to abortion services, women will be forced to turn to back alley, unsafe, and dangerous procedures. Reproductive rights are basic human rights. As an activist for social justice it is EXTREMELY important that the Morgentaler Clinic receive governmental funds for services. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Julie Mulherin","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89372241"},{"created_at":"2014-03-10T17:28:07Z","content":"Every woman should have the right to control what happens in their life and to their body.\r\n","like_count":0,"author_name":"Victoria Tsoulouhas","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/47066112"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T20:42:59Z","content":"This isn't just a women's rights issue. This is an issue for both women and men alike. This is moving backwards in our progress of providing safe healthcare and providing everyone with a choice for their bodies. It is called reproductive rights for a reason- no one should have the ability to take that away. NB, step up your game and starting supporting and helping to fund a necessary service in our province! Most places in NB offer free, safe alternatives to pregnancy; like in Ontario it is covered by OHIP. NB, taking away this clinic will NOT stop abortions- it will only cause abortions that are unsafe and that are behind closed doors. We will not stop fighting till our voices are heard. We will not be silenced!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Alisha Virmani","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78376208"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T20:00:21Z","content":"It is an issue of fundamental justice.  The wealthy in New Brunswick can go elsewhere and pay for abortions.  What about the women who do not have the financial means?  It is fundamentally discrimination.  We need seperation of church and state.  It is the 21st century so I am told, but one would not think that living in new Brunswick.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Erik Millett","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89549713"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T12:25:36Z","content":"To choose to have an abortion is a difficult choice...it should not be made more difficult.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Vicky Merritt Carr","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89359485"},{"created_at":"2014-04-12T19:39:39Z","content":"To provide women with a choice that is safe. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lane MacIntosh","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89480381"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T12:50:17Z","content":"Pour que toute femme ait le choix. Pour les droits humains, tout simplement.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Anik Fortier","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/75883581"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T15:23:04Z","content":"Because the New Brunswick government is basically breaking Federal law by not funding the abortions for women. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jennifer Jamieson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89622366"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T03:37:10Z","content":"Any woman, no matter where she lives, should have the right to choose what happens with her body. With this clinic closing, in NB that avenue is being closed off despite the Canada Health Act allowing women this choice. NB is in contravention of the law of Canada. I object to this strongly!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Nancy Law","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/32056405"},{"created_at":"2014-03-10T18:42:01Z","content":"For women and their choice to decide about their life and their body","like_count":0,"author_name":"nigam khanal","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/9074281"},{"created_at":"2014-04-12T00:05:30Z","content":"Any woman should have the right to an abortion if she so chooses.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Carrie McLong","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89416237"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T23:03:41Z","content":"Women have the right to choose. Every child a wanted, every mother a willing mother!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Haley McLean","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89302648"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T21:05:18Z","content":"I'm a family doctor, I see woman every day living through pregnancy or unwanted babies with lots of difficulty. I refer to Morgentaler often","like_count":0,"author_name":"Martine Theriault","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89667511"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T21:30:31Z","content":"Abortion is a woman's choice and must be accessible, safe and funded, as is all other health care.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sue Barrett","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89554783"},{"created_at":"2014-03-21T16:56:25Z","content":"It is time for NB to find itself on the right side of history. A woman has the right to do with her body as she chooses. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Mike McGinn","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/13142454"},{"created_at":"2014-04-12T13:58:53Z","content":"Wonen deserve the right to chose","like_count":0,"author_name":"Erica Steeves","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89458665"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T15:58:37Z","content":"This should be important to everyone.  It is their right to choose.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kalian Hiew","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89253481"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T16:37:50Z","content":"Because this service is important and should be accessible to women.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Cassandra Lynch","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89381496"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T15:32:51Z","content":"This is an important resource in the region.  And an important issue of social justice.","like_count":0,"author_name":"John deRoche","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/54877709"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T23:49:17Z","content":"women's rights","like_count":0,"author_name":"Amanda Thomas","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89415246"},{"created_at":"2014-03-10T22:01:54Z","content":"Womens Health should be important to EVERYONE. As a woman, it is especially important to me.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Elizabeth Vibert","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/74247453"},{"created_at":"2014-04-16T17:55:34Z","content":"This is important to all woman becuase every woman who gets pregnant DESERVES TO HAVE ALL OPTIONS OPEN TO HER, EVEN SAFE LEGAL ABORTIONS. Anyone who disagrees with this is a self-important asshole because your personal, religious \"moral\" beliefs do not trump a woman's right to PERSONAL BODILY AUTONOMY. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Petra Forsberg","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/petrashmetra"},{"created_at":"2014-04-15T03:22:40Z","content":"I am Pro Choice it is important for a woman to decide what to do with their own body and when it is appropriate, Trust Woman to make decisions","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jean-Pierre Forest","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/25277531"},{"created_at":"2014-03-10T13:48:39Z","content":"I think that its a woman right to have a abortion .","like_count":0,"author_name":"amy russell","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/85163635"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T17:29:33Z","content":"For the people without healthcare. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Alexandra Townsend","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89385869"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T13:54:07Z","content":"It is both the right thing to do and respects the Supreme Court's ruling that requiring proof of medical need is unconstitutional.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Hilary Young","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/61183563"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T15:06:56Z","content":"Women's right to safe affordable abortion without consent of others or medical necessity is a basic right.turn on the light NB gov!!!! We will not let this issues go un corrected,,,","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sarah Mallory wright","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89532410"},{"created_at":"2014-03-31T19:47:08Z","content":"The expense involved with getting an abortion is incredibly unfair, as is the requirement for two doctors to approve the procedure. This inserts a layer of religious authority that a woman needs to get through, unless she happens to know two doctors who don't follow those beliefs. This is simply wrong and, as a life long New Brunswicker, deeply embarrassing when people from other parts of Canada find out how backward we are.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Chris Spinney","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/88034023"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T17:52:12Z","content":"Responsibility begins at conception. Women are made responsible. For many, stigma and hardship also begin there. Those without the means should not be denied the right to make this very difficult \"choice\".   ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jeannie Malcolm","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89539123"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T19:26:07Z","content":"Because a woman has the right to choose","like_count":0,"author_name":"Laurent Carbonneau","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89547658"},{"created_at":"2014-04-12T21:33:47Z","content":"This is an essential medical service. Outrageous the option is being taken away due to financial reasons.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Tavis Latimer","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89487954"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T14:26:15Z","content":"I'm a man, and biologically speaking, I will never need an abortion personally. So, I can't really speak for or against it. However, I believe that it's healthier for women to be given the option. Let them decide. You want to keep that child? Great! Best of luck with your pregnancy! You don't feel ready yet and want to have it terminated in a safe, regulated, and organized environment, then that should be accessible as a basic health right.  ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Rayan Bouhlel","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89369974"},{"created_at":"2014-04-15T15:00:13Z","content":"the right of women to control our own bodies is a fundamental human right. Shame on the NB government for refusing to ensure this right is upheld.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jennifer Whiteside","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/29859450"},{"created_at":"2014-04-16T13:50:57Z","content":"I am a woman who supposedly lives in a democratic country where my rights are recognized","like_count":0,"author_name":"Bertha Power","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89881754"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T20:21:44Z","content":"Giving birth to a child is not a decision to be taken lightly. Raising a child is a responsibility like no other. A woman has the right in Canada to choose whether that is a responsibility she is able to assume. No child should be forced onto any mother and should be entitled to love and shelter in a nurturing home. Women must be ensured the right to choose. Please provide the necessary funding.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Rosanne Iland","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/12388662"},{"created_at":"2014-03-10T20:03:26Z","content":"every woman should have the right to choose. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Erika Foster","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/85205975"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T21:46:30Z","content":"Regardless of whether or not a person \"believes in\" abortion, or would ever consider having one themselves, it 