http://api.change.org/u/89998972"},{"created_at":"2014-04-16T15:22:11Z","content":"Before abortion was legalize, the consequence of \"home made\" abortion attempt was the number one cause of death for woman under 25 years of age.  As a health care professional, any thing that could lead back to such a threat to young woman is unacceptable.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Andr\u00e9e-Anne Larue","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/34794263"},{"created_at":"2014-03-11T19:57:24Z","content":"A woman should have access to safe medical care and the right to decide her own future.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Katherine MacDonald","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/85332062"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T23:18:55Z","content":"Women's rights are important for everyone ","like_count":0,"author_name":"cliff hughes","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89305636"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T20:17:59Z","content":"If this clinic closes there will be only one clinic east of Montreal. That is profoundly unfair to the women of eastern Canada and it will lead desperate people to take desperate measures. This clinic deserves to be funded in the interests of the health, safety and fundamental rights of all women in Canada.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Catherine Higgins","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/26951824"},{"created_at":"2014-04-16T18:50:29Z","content":"Abortion is not criminal in this country, the government should not create barriers to access. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Alison Moore","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/65139110"},{"created_at":"2014-03-14T16:31:24Z","content":"It is violating rights and freedoms. As a woman, I am offended that this current regulation is in effect. Ridiculous! ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Delana Hockey","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/85712257"},{"created_at":"2014-04-12T21:25:51Z","content":"All women have a right to decide what happens to their bodies and society has the obligation to make it safe! We don't need to go back to the dark ages and back alleys ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Karen Morrison","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89487517"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T15:51:31Z","content":"All women in Canada should have equal opportunity to exercise their reproductive rights.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Pat Daley","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/12436796"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T19:59:01Z","content":"Because all women should have equal access to abortion.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Nicola Cassidy","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89274701"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T11:12:46Z","content":"No Canadian should lack access to health care because of their postal code.","like_count":0,"author_name":"L Birmingham","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/52527690"},{"created_at":"2014-03-10T21:44:15Z","content":"I wish I had known sooner that this unconstitutional action was in place. I would have been active for 25 years to right this wrong.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Heather Good","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/16704475"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T01:28:17Z","content":"I want the option to be there for peace of mind ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Cloe Lecours","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89316251"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T20:58:46Z","content":"All women deserve the right to choose ! Don't forget the women of New Brunswick and PEI","like_count":0,"author_name":"Mary Turnbull","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89552831"},{"created_at":"2014-03-10T12:33:00Z","content":"All women deserve equal rights over their body and how they choose to live their lives.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Janelle MacDonnell","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/85157063"},{"created_at":"2014-04-12T16:17:36Z","content":"Because access to abortion (not only legal but also financial) and women's right (and economic possibility) to control their own body is a basic human right. That this is still not acknowledged in certain parts of Canada is a shame.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Mireille Fournier","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89467207"},{"created_at":"2014-04-15T12:10:49Z","content":"Women deserve a choice","like_count":0,"author_name":"Norma Chase","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/14806151"},{"created_at":"2014-03-11T16:19:06Z","content":"no one has the right to tell a woman what is best for them. Our Provincial Gov't should be ashamed that they are trying to make women into baby factories. The Gov't has no business making decisions about my body - EVER","like_count":0,"author_name":"Heather McCabe","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/31900744"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T20:11:09Z","content":"People with the ability to bear children should be the sole deciders of whether they choose to give birth to the child or not.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Geoff Geofferson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/34105918"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T22:10:04Z","content":"To have the right, as a woman, to have a choice.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Natasha LeBlanc","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89293498"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T23:23:41Z","content":"Every women deserves the right to an adoration if she needs one or not.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jessie Scott-Henderson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89306516"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T02:07:19Z","content":"Women's health is an important issue, and access to safe and timely abortions is a human right, especially in Canada. I was shocked to see this story coming out of New Brunswick, my birth province. Having these hurdles in the way of a woman obtaining an abortion is unreasonable and unethical. Help the province, help these women.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jason McConnery","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/52629123"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T03:19:19Z","content":"female reproductive rights, and human rights in general","like_count":0,"author_name":"Veronique Gauthier","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/50512588"},{"crea