d ownership of their bodies! Basic women's rights.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Alice Hemming","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/91931484"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T04:06:52Z","content":"WOMEN'S RIGHTS","like_count":0,"author_name":"amna khurshid","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/26081199"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T20:43:06Z","content":"Universal Healthcare is a right, not a privilege.  I don't want any of our women risking their lives by trying to abort with their own devices.  ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Chris McCurdy","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89664341"},{"created_at":"2014-04-28T02:18:57Z","content":"Morgentaler's clinic is being forced to close because access to abortion in New Brunswick is restricted to those who can pay, and the clinic wouldn't turn away anyone who needed an abortion.  This is a shameful way to treat Dr. Morgentaler's legacy.  ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Finn Manniche","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/38630406"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T03:10:26Z","content":"As a family medicine resident at Dalhousie in Saint John, I really fear that this closure will negatively effect my patients' ability to receive access to safe family planning.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Robin Clouston","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/21808606"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T14:31:21Z","content":"fundamental human right","like_count":0,"author_name":"Craig Martin","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89370443"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T11:16:17Z","content":"La libert\u00e9 de choix des femmes est incontournable.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jean Sauvageau","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89610693"},{"created_at":"2014-03-11T15:13:32Z","content":"This regulation is violation  and unconstitutional.","like_count":0,"author_name":"kim vose jones","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/60524721"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T12:52:59Z","content":"It is not acceptable to dictate what women do with thier bodies through bad legislation, especially when it comes to personal and difficult choices such as abortion. This has to stop immediately.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Dana Arsenault","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89618139"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T17:41:31Z","content":"Women should have the right to legal safe abortion, any attempts to limit our attempts need to be stopped immediately!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Cindy McDonnell","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/2966493"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T12:45:51Z","content":"Every woman should have the right to decide on her life and future.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Arlene Erven","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36074860"},{"created_at":"2014-04-08T03:54:57Z","content":"Don't take away a woman's reproductive options. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Alannah Smith","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/88878086"},{"created_at":"2014-03-10T05:04:20Z","content":"because all women should have the right to their bodies ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Chelsea Charelson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/85131890"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T21:13:43Z","content":"This is important because unwanted children are born and someone has to pick up the pieces for this. Tax increases as well for social assistance costs.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Anne Matos","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/2052410"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T22:53:01Z","content":"You are not allowed to make two provinces' choices wether or not they want a child.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Gabrielle Gagnon","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89558697"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T15:48:18Z","content":"Grow up, gov.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Step Taylor","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/86899171"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T15:14:43Z","content":"I believe it is essential that women should have EQUAL access to reproductive healthcare. Reproductive rights do need to be a priority, and the current state of this affair is a poor reflection on our current government's position and support for women. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Brandy Peters","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/56126050"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T17:52:05Z","content":"It is my body and my right.  I shouldn't be penalized because my chromosomes are XX instead of XY","like_count":0,"author_name":"Hannah Doull","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89387780"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T19:40:02Z","content":"As I heard a gentleman say recently: \"If I wanted to have a vasectomy, I wouldn't need two doctors to provide permission - just one to have the time to do it.\" Why should female reproductive rights be different? \r\nThis closure will also result in the deaths and endangerment of many women who will be forced to seek out alternatives to safe, legal, affordable, and accessible abortions.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Linda Gallant","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/12835721"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T23:49:41Z","content":"WOMEN SHOULD HAVE A CHOICE","like_count":0,"author_name":"Chantal Michaud","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89415265"},{"created_at":"2014-03-24T15:56:22Z","content":"It is important to keep women's rights to decide about having a baby or not ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Linda Trachy","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/87166984"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T23:27:52Z","content":"Access to safe abortion services is necessary. Currently, hospital abortion requires the approval of 2 doctors, and this is unacceptable.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sue Hughson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/19521297"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T23:32:50Z","content":"I believe that women have the right to choose what they do with their body and a governmental body does not have the right to decide what is best. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kieran Mathieson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/28962609"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T19:12:43Z","content":"Because everyone woman should have the right to choose for her own body. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Tina Collins","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/69980803"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T19:42:46Z","content":"It is a woman's right to choose plain and simple not two doctors opinions that it is medically necessary.  To  those that say use birth control well guess what birth control fails all the time even when used correctly (look at the statistics).","like_count":0,"author_name":"ronda mattson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/59083462"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T20:16:39Z","content":"Because we've come too far to be pushed back.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Brandi Carnes","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89550633"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T21:10:57Z","content":"Women deserve a choice. We are too far behind the times.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sue Davis","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/33810658"},{"created_at":"2014-04-15T08:40:45Z","content":"I am a Canadian woman. I believe 50% of New Brunswick residents are women.  Existing services in New Brunswick hospitals will not be able to handle the demand for abortion care if the Morgenthaler clinic closes.  That means a significant number of female residents will not be served. This represents systematic discrimination against women. Although I do not need an abortion now, I have needed one in the past.  Thank heavens I live in a province where I had relatively easy access and full funding for my care.  I can't imagine living in New Brunswick with such \"backwards\" attitudes of the members of the legislative assemby.  Shame on you for not respecting the legal rights of women!!!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Ruth Brighouse","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/32796530"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T19:59:05Z","content":"Abortion should be an option for any woman, regardless of where they live, and I feel this clinic should be supported by the government since it is the only place to get an abortion in New Brunswick.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Will McArthur","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89274711"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T23:27:53Z","content":"Because women's health is important.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Alexandra Martin","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/11015103"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T21:49:59Z","content":"This is a medical procedure like so many others that women should have easy, non-judgemental access to.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jennifer Richardson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89671613"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T14:15:54Z","content":"The restrictions placed on obtaining proper and timely reproductive support for NB and PEI women are outdated and serve only as a punishment for women. HELP!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Isabelle Robichaud","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89242974"},{"created_at":"2014-04-18T01:17:47Z","content":"Human rights","like_count":0,"author_name":"mary sue rankin","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/60104803"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T15:08:07Z","content":"Everyone should have access to free abortion services. This argument has been had before, and it is not a want but a need.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Natasha Melbrew","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/15656963"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T15:39:58Z","content":"my body. my choice. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Danika Carleton","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89251882"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T15:33:02Z","content":"I feel that it is a woman's choice.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Joshua Munn","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/57730296"},{"created_at":"2014-04-15T12:25:55Z","content":"Safety","like_count":0,"author_name":"Scott Jones","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89726956"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T15:06:29Z","content":"Were 2014, I think women deserve this right to choose what to do wih their bodies, rather than have a biased doctor give them the okay or not.... ","like_count":0,"author_name":"nicole currie","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89620634"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T20:09:51Z","content":"Because shutting down an abortion clinic isn't going to stop women from wanting or needing abortions, it's only going to put the women in danger of hurting or killing themselves. Access to safe  abortions is a right. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lydia Bloomfield","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/23409406"},{"created_at":"2014-03-11T20:02:03Z","content":"This is totally discriminatory for underwaged women, and violates the Supreme Court decision. Women's choice is critical to healthy families.","like_count":0,"author_name":"carol scott","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/32227032"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T18:09:52Z","content":"I believe as a woman we should have the choice and have the means available to us","like_count":0,"author_name":"Angela Mehan","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89543176"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T00:17:23Z","content":"Because no one should have the right to tell me what I can and can't do with my body.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Chrissie MacNeil","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89561917"},{"created_at":"2014-03-11T04:26:07Z","content":"Because abortion is a legal medical service under Canadian law. NB women should have rights equal to other women in Canada.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Patricia Kipping","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/8155019"},{"created_at":"2014-04-12T13:30:16Z","content":"While I don't believe abortion should be used as a form of birth control, every woman has a circumstance in which they choose this option.  Every woman deserves to not have this choice taken away!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Nicole Lemay","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89456996"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T09:47:06Z","content":"It's the law.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Susan McAdam","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37077179"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T18:36:22Z","content":"reduces self harm/ reduces the number of single mother/ teen pregnancies/ should be just as much a right as it is for a man to get a vasectomy/ ","like_count":0,"author_name":"JoLynn Aitken","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89391712"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T23:06:23Z","content":"Let's make sure we don't go backwards.  We fought long and hard for these rights and for equal access.\r\n\r\n","like_count":0,"author_name":"mindy weiss","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/23059299"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T16:58:01Z","content":"BECAUSE REPRODUCTIVE RIGHTS ARE BASIC HUMAN RIGHTS. WHAT CENTURY ARE WE LIVING IN???","like_count":0,"author_name":"Nicole Aksu","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89538927"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T21:06:13Z","content":"Women have the right to choose and not have two doctors determine if her choice is correct in their eyes.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Cathy Ayotte","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89553483"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T15:56:52Z","content":"People have the right to choose. Removing that choice  is taking away fundamental rights!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Colin Clark","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/40430564"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T00:54:56Z","content":"I am Pro Choice!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Darla McKay","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/7588672"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T15:59:36Z","content":"freedom of choice","like_count":0,"author_name":"Brad Waddingham","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89626473"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T23:05:57Z","content":"This is a right that should be universal.  ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Gail Waller","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89303079"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T02:27:36Z","content":"it is our turn to be there for them","like_count":0,"author_name":"Charlene Seaman","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/46942836"},{"created_at":"2014-04-15T21:45:28Z","content":"As a young woman from New Brunswick, I am saddened and embarassed by the state of the law in New Brunswick and the impending closure of the clinic. You can, and must, do better New Brunswick. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Koren Thomson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/15080918"}]}
