ld be able to access free abortion at their local hospital.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Debra Hubner","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/64417752"},{"created_at":"2014-03-12T00:46:39Z","content":"Limiting access to abortion services does nothing except for hurt women. It has never been a problem for people who can afford an abortion to get one, however for those who cannot.. well desperate women will do desperate things, and that is terrifying. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jaden Fitzherbert","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/47089781"},{"created_at":"2014-03-11T12:28:57Z","content":"This is important because it discrimates against any person who cannot afford 700$ who an emergency. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kaylie Burke","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/75145773"},{"created_at":"2014-03-10T16:45:18Z","content":"This is a human right, especially in medically necessary situations. I am an atheist, and there are enough children to adopt in the world already.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Gavin Billings","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/85177028"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T17:19:39Z","content":"I lived in NB for five years, and helped protect the women from outside the clinic a few mornings as a volunteer. Closing is not a sane option. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Stephanie Yorke","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/58048812"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T11:37:10Z","content":"I believe in a woman's right to choose. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lesley Guravich","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/58831082"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T15:45:19Z","content":"There is a need to have a private clinic in the Atlantic region.  This is a personal decision for any woman and there should be support from the government","like_count":0,"author_name":"Marg Seaman","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89377040"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T16:10:17Z","content":"I believe women should have the right to judge whether it is the right time for them to h