iting that women need the abortion \"medically necessary\"? Make it legal, accessible and free to low income women, and we might become a better society!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sara Wilkinson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/50299561"},{"created_at":"2014-05-30T01:36:17Z","content":"Deciding to go with an abortion is hard enough -- it is completely the choice of whomever wishes to receive one.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Ethan Lewis","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/102988190"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T21:01:26Z","content":"Facilities should be available for those who make their choices.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Andrew James  Paterson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/5095033"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T00:16:25Z","content":"Its a health thing","like_count":0,"author_name":"Aaron Volk","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89311287"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T12:17:26Z","content":"I am a New Brunswicker and I believe safe, accessible publicly funded abortion is a basic right of Canadian women. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Heather Copp","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89615414"},{"created_at":"2014-04-15T12:50:24Z","content":"Woman's rights and it's 2014, keep your church out of my medical appts!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Martha Donovan","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/86780844"},{"created_at":"2014-03-24T11:30:18Z","content":"Because someone else's religious belief system should not be the reason I can't explore all options in the situation of an unwanted pregnancy. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Danielle Cooper","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/2580427"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T17:30:06Z","content":"Women should have the right to choose whether or not they want an abortion.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kassandra Myer","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89385907"},{"created_at":"2014-03-15T04:48:24Z","content":"Social welfare is funded by the state whether before or after birth. ","like_count":0,"aut