nt":0,"author_name":"Chantal LeBlanc","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/3596338"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T19:09:16Z","content":"Pro-Choice or No-Choice","like_count":0,"author_name":"Nathan Ingraham","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89268802"},{"created_at":"2014-04-15T13:31:12Z","content":"the removal of these services will primarily affect already marginalized women. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Anna Frey","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/46752605"},{"created_at":"2014-04-16T14:30:55Z","content":"I practice safe sex. Why should I have to carry a child I don't want should the worst happen?","like_count":0,"author_name":"Emilie S.","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/43328902"},{"created_at":"2014-04-17T14:42:19Z","content":"Women have the right to choose what happens to their bodies!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Shyanne Richard","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/90008640"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T16:23:05Z","content":"Canada's highest court determined that people have the right to decide when and if to bear children. If women in New Brunswick do not have access to affordable abortions and they need 2 doctors to deem it \"medically necessary,\" this right is not being provided.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jessica Carson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/547557"},{"created_at":"2014-03-11T21:41:35Z","content":"Regulated bodies remain slaves to a society's dictates.  ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Emma Cunningham","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/50513820"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T19:52:57Z","content":"Justice, human/women's rights","like_count":0,"author_name":"John Cleghorn","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89549267"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T21:56:02Z","content":"Because I am a woman!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Avery Kaye","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/69992667"},{"created_at":"2014-04-15T00:31:58Z","content":"This is important to me because I believe it is a crime to take away a women's choice.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Laura Bellussi","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/71798437"},{"created_at":"2014-04-12T16:50:51Z","content":"Women deserve the right to choose. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Tyler LeBlanc","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89469607"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T10:20:35Z","content":"Woman's Right to Choose; current situation violates Women's Rights, per Supreme Court ruling in Morgantaler case decision.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Shane Ervin","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89604463"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T17:15:16Z","content":"As a progressive person, I believe that it is a basic human right to have autonomy over one's body. Parenthood, pregnancy and giving birth is not to be taken lightly.  Women should have the ability to choose whether they want these experiences.  Their choices should be made and executed without fear and oppression. Let's stop living in archaic ideologies and start moving forward.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Rebecca McKinnon","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/74078430"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T23:25:36Z","content":"The only requirement to schedule an abortion should be to say \"Hello, I'd like to schedule an abortion.\" Control of one's own fertility is a basic human right. Abortion is part of that control, and it is a part that belongs, not to the government, but to the women who want and require it. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"S.E. Loftus","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/3593479"},{"created_at":"2014-04-16T01:03:33Z","content":"All women should have access to free and safe abortion services. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Ashley Milbury","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/39440830"},{"created_at":"2014-03-20T00:56:36Z","content":"Because women ought to have reproductive autonomy regardless of their income.","like_count":0,"author_name":"David Ackerson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/86643534"},{"created_at":"2014-03-13T01:59:40Z","content":"Its my body","like_count":