.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Bruce Newman","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89368670"},{"created_at":"2014-04-29T13:30:50Z","content":"Women's right to bodily autonomy is enshrined in CEDAW, to which Canada is a signatory. Refusing women access to terminations of pregnancies they don't want violates Canada's constitution & sets a poor example to the world.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Vanessa Farr","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/2851281"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T20:22:47Z","content":"This is something women have been fighting for forever in this province. It is the right thing to do.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Peter Hall","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/44377456"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T21:58:04Z","content":"It is disgusting and outrageous that New Brunswick is not funding services at the clinic. Keep abortions accessible and SAFE for everybody. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Emilia Deil","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89291672"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T23:38:29Z","content":"Women need access to safe abortions.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jilian Van Kester","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89308548"},{"created_at":"2014-04-12T03:52:49Z","content":"Erica Vienneau","like_count":0,"author_name":"Erica Vienneau","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78800233"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T14:22:08Z","content":"<a href=\"http://www.theguardian.pe.ca/News/Local/2011-11-10/article-Because\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://www.theguardian.pe.ca/News/Local/2011-11-10/article-Because</a> of this! 2802198/Women-turning-to-desperate-measures-due-to-lack-of-abortion-services/1","like_count":0,"author_name":"Carmel maher","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37013022"},{"created_at":"2014-03-21T06:03:17Z","content":"Woman should be in control of there healthcare not a bunch of old white men or religious fanatics. If you are going to deny woman free choice in healthcare the same should be applied to men, no penis pumps and no drugs like Viagra!","like_count":0,"author_name":"judith bodie","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/62354293"},{"created_at":"2014-04-15T16:03:51Z","content":"Pro-choice, pro-education, pro-reproductive health.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Andrea Donnery","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/13460254"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T19:44:09Z","content":"All women should have the right to choose, regardless of their financial situation. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Hazel Richardson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/3613249"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T23:19:21Z","content":"If women can't afford an abortion, how can they afford to raise a child.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Gillian Matheson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89305724"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T23:26:11Z","content":"This clinic services individuals with the need within my hometown. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"William Gertler","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89307008"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T00:18:46Z","content":"Women are not to be held hostage to anyone with respect to choices they need to make regarding their bodies, their health. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Cindy Ross","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89561967"},{"created_at":"2014-04-20T23:05:24Z","content":"This is extremely important because it is an equity issue.  Women of financial means alway have access to abortions.  They can afford to pay expenses that take them beyond their local community.  \r\n\r\nAbortion is a medical procedure and women have a right to this procedure if they so choose.  \r\n\r\n","like_count":0,"author_name":"Rosemary Dale","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/90263394"},{"created_at":"2014-04-12T11:47:59Z","content":"Because I believe in choice, in equality, in women's rights, and in safe medical procedures. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Isabelle Daigle","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89450218"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T15:44:26Z","content":"To ease concerns of women and all involved","like_count":0,"author_name":"Gilbert   Titus Harmer","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89252317"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T21:07:39Z","content":"All women have the RIGHT to this, regardless of other people's beliefs. Closing this would be a disgrace and a huge step backward in women's right, and I'm a man saying all of this. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Oliver Crook","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89284933"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T04:48:47Z","content":"Many of my family members and friends are women","like_count":0,"author_name":"Julien Martin","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89197333"},{"created_at":"2014-04-13T19:10:31Z","content":"Access to safe abortions is as important as safe birthing places. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"David Vaillancourt","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89546345"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T00:58:28Z","content":"Because I am pro choice","like_count":0,"author_name":"Clare Lewis","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/58678002"},{"created_at":"2014-03-12T00:56:45Z","content":"Access to safe, affordable, and timely abortion services is a human health-care right.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Mary Mifflen","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/6468643"},{"created_at":"2014-03-12T01:44:39Z","content":"It's important because I am a woman who has aspirations that do not include becoming a parent.   Because the world is overpopulated and we need to reduce that 7 billion. Because I believe abortion is being responsible if you don't want the child.  Because there are far too many children waiting for adoption so putting another into that system is irresponsible of the individual and the government (blame depends on the legal restraints toward abortion).  Because costing the women who choose abortion does not create a healthy economy and disadvantages the individual (may not be able to afford condoms/other birth control for some time due to the abortion fee).  Because women are paid significantly less than men but the tab falls to us.  Because the government should concern themselves with the willingness of people to leave the province for far less reason.  Because I breathe, I have rights, and I have a life of my own that needs to be taken seriously by the government. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jennifer Coburn","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/22030864"},{"created_at":"2014-04-12T20:43:31Z","content":"Women's bodily autonomy should not be compromised. Her body, her choice.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Donna Harris","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/56422330"},{"created_at":"2014-04-18T05:16:45Z","content":"This has been a democratic freedom for 25 yrs. to stop funding now is allowing Harper's fascism to control.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Maureen R","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/29988051"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T21:22:44Z","content":"The New Brunswick government is conducting an illegal campaign to suppress women's right to abortion as provided by the Health Act.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Christopher Hart","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89286964"},{"created_at":"2014-03-21T12:54:43Z","content":"This is Canada! We should be showing USA what really needs to happen to allow women access to good reproductive health. Don't follow in the USA footsteps and start making vital health care even more hard to get like in the States! I'm very disappointed in Canada. The government has money to find these services if half of them can use this money to pay for their vacations! My god. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Taylor Gray","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/24981454"},{"created_at":"2014-03-22T13:46:48Z","content":"Restrictions like these are definitely unconstitutional and those pro death culture know this.   Let us pray that our dear country return to The Lord's Prayer.... Thy Will Be Done on earth as it is in Heaven ! Let us pray to protect the children whom God created ! ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Diane  Marie Maillard","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/30250788"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T00:52:23Z","content":"becuase women's health is an important issue and abortion is a woman's right. how dare they remove two entire provinces access to safe conditions for a procedure like that.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Hayley Halloran","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/2671445"},{"created_at":"2014-04-17T22:33:06Z","content":"A woman's legal right to choose.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Georgia Dryden","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/90038343"},{"created_at":"2014-04-17T13:45:39Z","content":"It is appalling that in this day and age in a free country like Canada that it would be difficult for women to make reproductive choices for themselves.  Disgusted with the government for refusing to fund this clinic and making it a requirement for 2 doctors to sign to deem it medically necessary for a woman to get an abortion at a hospital in New Brunswick, the only other option .  ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Cathy Mannall","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/59069553"},{"created_at":"2014-04-20T11:29:13Z","content":"because common sense","like_count":0,"author_name":"ftlmg trgfgc","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/90225546"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T15:27:50Z","content":"Women have a right to fully funded reproductive health services including abortion.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Mark Gold","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/1863997"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T15:40:28Z","content":"Because every woman deserves the right to decide what to do with their body!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Vikki Hallihan","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89251935"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T10:48:02Z","content":"A woman's right to her own body.\r\n","like_count":0,"author_name":"Alice Costello","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89608484"},{"created_at":"2014-04-10T18:35:58Z","content":"Reproductive rights are human rights, and access to abortion clinics are vital to those rights. ","lik