se.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jennifer Sears","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89425348"},{"created_at":"2014-04-12T03:31:16Z","content":"Women should have the right to safely terminate a pregnancy if they so choose and this should be covered so no woman is ever in a situation they don't want to be in. Desperate women will do desperate things. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kelly Moore","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/32608648"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T22:37:36Z","content":"Because the law says a woman alone has the right to choose whether or not she has a baby and our government is imposing barriers to access to abortions.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jeff Roach","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/53455491"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T05:04:47Z","content":"Access to reproductive health care is vital. It must be made available to all.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sophie Morgan","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/30495324"},{"created_at":"2014-04-22T16:02:45Z","content":"Abortions can be had with or without a clinic, but with a clinic is the best way, and a clinic where the choice is yours is ideal. Funding the only private abortion clinic in the area is just a good idea, no matter how you look at it.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Clinton Guthrie","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/90415046"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T14:37:21Z","content":"Women in New Brunswick have the right to reproductive health services. Your government has the duty to provide access to it.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Gerri Thorsteinson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89371005"},{"created_at":"2014-03-25T14:12:48Z","content":"Because every women should have the choice.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jessica Lavigne","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/87276067"},{"created_at":"2014-04-12T00:32:14Z","content":"This news makes me embarrassed to say that I used to live in such a backwards province. Access to abortion is NECESSARY. ","like_count":0,"author