ldren of their own who would desperately want that child.  But I realize there are many reasons why an abortion may be the best decision (financial, severe health risks, harmful living conditions, abuse, rape, etc etc), and every woman has the right to make that decision for herself.\nRegardless of where you land of the Pro-Life-Pro-Choice spectrum, every single person in this province should have acess to safe and sterile conditions for any and all types of medical procedures.  Be Pro-Woman - don't let unsafe conditions cause women to die simply because their province couldn't look past the moral controversy and see through to the glaringly inhumane (and immoral, if you will) decision to deny proper medical facilities and procedures to women.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lisa Steeves","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89411996"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T23:14:23Z","content":"This is un fundamental right in Canada, we need to go forward as a society, not backward!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Hugues Morin","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89412978"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T23:21:53Z","content":"women's rights","like_count":0,"author_name":"siobhan boyle","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/89413474"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T18:46:09Z","content":"Because this is a difficult choice to make, and hospitals are awful.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Rebecca Rustin","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/2867370"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T03:56:08Z","content":"Let's not go back to back-alley abortions with coat-hangers.  If someone needs to terminate a pregnancy, they will find a way, lets make sure that there is a safe place for them to turn.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Shelagh Sutherland","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/47105311"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T04:08:34Z","content":"ALL Canadian women have a right to access safe abortions.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Elizabeth Hogan","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/47007484"},{"created_at