nge.org/u/89507927"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T22:59:58Z","content":"It's time for change. I am New Brunswick-born and this matters.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lillian Wight","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/2576658"},{"created_at":"2014-04-06T22:33:32Z","content":"Having safe and easy access to full reproductive services is a nationally legislated right for women in Canada, and yet the Maritime provinces continue to support unconstitutional policy that deliberately limits this access. Abortion is part of health care, not an elective or extraneous procedure. 1 in 3 women will have an abortion in their lifetime. As a future doctor, if I don't support women's access to this service, then I'm not doing my job to 1/3 of the patients I will meet. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kathryn Wood","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/88715061"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T03:27:28Z","content":"This is a matter of women's rights and safety. New Brunswick must not allow ourself to take this dangerous step backward in women's health!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Amanda Hensey","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/17169343"},{"created_at":"2014-04-12T11:28:09Z","content":"i believe women should have the right to choose for themselves and have a safe place to go should they decide to terminate. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Shannon Shum","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/22240349"},{"created_at":"2014-04-14T01:46:27Z","content":"Only the woman can decide, not religious nutcases trying to impose their beliefs on others.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Greta Jansen","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/3309728"},{"created_at":"2014-03-10T16:09:55Z","content":"Abortions should be freely available to ALL women! ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Michelle McLauchlan","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/85172033"},{"created_at":"2014-04-11T14:43:07Z","content":"Womens' personal choices should not be needlessly obstructed to suit an ideology. Womens' Bodies, Womens' Choice